import Vue from 'vue'
import App from './App.vue'
import VueRouter from 'vue-router' 
import {Routes} from './router/index'

const router = new VueRouter({
  routes: Routes,
  mode: "history"
})

Vue.config.productionTip = false


Vue.use(VueRouter)
new Vue({
  router: router,
  render: h => h(App),
}).$mount('#app')
